{"tid":397281,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"香港公屋  蘇·半山","createTime":"2017-09-12T11:08:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-15T16:34:03.000Z","uid":2104,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"60c794e21a2f958244ce5e166e13f746a0c482f2","tid":397281,"uid":2104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T11:08:12.000Z","msg":"話說原來我已經放低咗部相機幾年...<br />\n今日整理一下個Hard disk先發現原來我都有份記錄香港<br />\n呢個post啲相係攝於2008年夏天<br />\n果一日我專登帶住部相機去到當年仲未折嘅蘇屋邨<br />\n當時我喺度諗 影一啲相 為呢個依山而建嘅公共屋邨出一分力 <br />\n用相片做返少少記錄<br />\n當時我為攝影初哥 <br />\n用嘅係SONY A200 鏡用18-250<br />\n影得唔好 敬請勿插"},{"pid":"6137f3028d73f25898e9c39d4525a9de13ed8abc","tid":397281,"uid":38970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T11:08:54.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"9c7a9f83ab954859a76fa39ca856a9bf68878e87","tid":397281,"uid":2104,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T11:10:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/12/190923_3853607c11aef6e33955ba53f3681af5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F12%2F190923_3853607c11aef6e33955ba53f3681af5.jpg&h=f414fa0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/12/191010_f32cd1241ac5c9db8dabb1d0b98477b3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F12%2F191010_f32cd1241ac5c9db8dabb1d0b98477b3.jpg&h=e6997741&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/12/191030_c22a35c96e54585295157ec42c4daaf9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F12%2F191030_c22a35c96e54585295157ec42c4daaf9.jpg&h=90f32da9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/12/190924_3853607c11aef6e33955ba53f3681af5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F12%